{"tid":654923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲少女遭輪姦 父母討公道 兇徒打人兼燒死少女","createTime":"2018-05-06T05:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T11:09:49.000Z","uid":51701,"like":347,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"50bfbf0b4ec71876102c23f3e38b39f2bbf793e5","tid":654923,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"印度一名16歲少女被綁架輪姦，其父母為她尋求公義時，遭多名男子暴打，該名少女被燒死。警方拘捕14名男子，但涉案主要人物仍然在逃。<br />\n事發於印度東部賈坎德邦（Jharkhand state）一條村莊。該名少女的父母外出參加婚禮時，有人闖入其家中把她擄走。警方指兩名男子在一個樹林把少女輪姦，少女回家後告訴父母，其父母向村中長老討公道，要求懲罰犯案者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長老要求犯案者做100次仰臥起坐（sit-ups），及罰款5萬盧布（750美元）。犯案者非常憤怒，發動支持者暴打少女的父母，有兩人闖入其家中把少女活活燒死。<br />\n警方表示，事件牽涉18人，當局拘捕了14人，其中一名把少女燒死的罪犯在逃。數名村中長老因執行私刑和篡改證據等罪名被落案起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/95044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F95044&d=sGwUIirdB4qypkm10ixhJqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=43330225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/95044</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係中國，又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc372c074dd9d37a7d66d62a04af16b5cbdf2273","tid":654923,"uid":19360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae2d9bb89d72c45ca11682b5eb3e801aa15ab7a","tid":654923,"uid":65128,"like":327,"dislike":1,"score":326,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ca72eba215ecd62164570f6a1cb06bb9d12cf44","tid":654923,"uid":18251,"like":150,"dislike":2,"score":148,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"痴燃線國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94a657fa8056edba320ff7400a250ce197cc931","tid":654923,"uid":77805,"like":603,"dislike":4,"score":599,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:36:57.00